file_content.text: You lost? Just go back the way you came--the controls should be there.
Better get to that scout. Tell Audra I said hi!
Looks like a combine came through the wall....
Don't come over here! She'll follow you!
Whoo! Look at all those bodies! ...That sounded bad, didn't it?
Got in a few shots with a welding torch. Ran out of gas, though.
Lot of water coming if that dam breaks. Wish I'd worn better shoes.
Welcome back. Garith's waiting to shake your hand.
I'll take care of the shield. You take care of the walkers. Fair deal?
I'll talk to the civs. Let 'em down gently if all this turns to rubble.
The Bothan. Talk to him. Ugh....
Bothawui's probably real pretty when it's not on fire.
